<section class="fullpage about bottom-edge" id="section-about">
  <header class="header__section">
    <h3 class="title__section letter-spacing">
      Services
    </h3>
  </header>

  <article class="about__service" id="service-consultation">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Style Consultation
      </h4>
    </header>

    <p class="service">
      A one-on-one conversation either in person, or over the phone. This is a time for us to determine your true style, outline your needs, your wants, and a budget. From that, I will make a game plan for us to review together that will bring clarity to the process.
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service service__multi" id="service-on-call-stylist">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        On Call Stylist
      </h4>
    </header>
    <div class="title__pricing">
      <span class="pricing__amount pricing__amount--primary">$595 a month with a 6 month commitment.</span>
      <span class="pricing__amount">$995 for couples.</span>
    </div>

    <p class="sub-service service__communication"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>Ongoing Communication:​</em></span> A monthly 1.5 hour at home consultation to discuss your budget, schedule, needs, and wants along with a closet refresh. This will ensure that you are constantly prepared for school events, charity dinners, luncheons, vacations, or anything else that gets thrown your way. It also ensures that you’re constantly analyzing your buys and purging what isn’t working to find the perfect balance.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__shopping"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>Consistent Shopping:</em></span> A personalized shop list, based off of your seasonal mood board,  will be sent monthly,  and constantly updated, along with the usual local pull items brought to your house when applicable.  I will update you to include sales/promos to save you money when I can (you know I love a good deal!!). This will give you the option to shop at your own pace and add on a few items at a time, rather than a large shop all at once.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__styling">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Continued Styling:</em></span>​ A monthly at home, 2 hour, fit/styling appointment when your shopping list arrives to cultivate killer looks and gather pictures for your future reference.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__availability">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Constant Communication:</em></span>​ You can text, FaceTime, or call whenever for help in a pinch! Whether you’re getting dressed in the morning for work, in the evening for date night, or need an interview outfit, I’ll make myself available to get you where you need to go looking and feeling your best!
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__conditions">
      <em>Out of town shopping is not included in this, or any packages, as I must charge a 15% commission rate when traveling in order to account for added costs.</em>
    </p>
  </article>

