  <article class="about__service" id="service-packing">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Travel Packing
      </h4>
    </header>
        <div class="title__pricing">
      <span class="pricing__amount pricing__amount--primary">$115 an hour</span>
    </div>
    <p class="service">
      We all have difficulty packing, and most women (as well as more than a few men!) are chronic over-packers. I will help you determine the pieces that will allow for maximum versatility on any trip. I’ll help eliminate the time and stress of packing and organizing your suitcase so that you can focus your pre-trip time on more important things. <span class="fake__break">Whether it’s a business trip or a beach vacation, your wardrobe will be personalized according to destination, weather forecast, and any planned events on your itinerary. Your included outfits will be pictured and outlined in order to take all of the deliberation and stress out of getting dressed, and keep your attention where it matters most.</span>
    </p>
  </article>

  <article class="about__service service__multi" id="service-virtual-styling">
    <header class="header__service">
      <h4 class="title__service letter-spacing">
        Virtual Styling
      </h4>
    </header>
    <div class="title__pricing">
      <span class="pricing__amount pricing__amount--primary">$1475</span>
    </div>

    <p class="sub-service service__virtual-consultation"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>New Client Consultation:​</em></span> A one hour FaceTime call to get to know you and your lifestyle. We will “walk through” your closet together to assess needs, wants, and items that are ready to purge! This is really a time for me to get to know you so that I can thoughtfully and intentionally build your wardrobe. We will get clear on the process and outline a game plan including budget and schedule.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__mood-board">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Custom Mood Board:</em></span>​ I will send a customized mood/styling board that will include outfit examples, proportion updates, and styling advice for us to review together. I love to work collaboratively to provide the best outcome, so I will explain my thought process while you provide specific feedback to ensure we are on the same page. I will make any necessary edits before we begin shopping.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__shopping-list"><span class="title__sub-service"><em>Consistent Shopping:</em></span> I will send you a personalized shop list of items for you to order at your own pace. Once items are ordered, we will jump on a FaceTime call to discuss fit along with styling and outfitting options, to ensure that each item integrates seamlessly into your existing wardrobe.
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__availability">
      <span class="title__sub-service"><em>Constant Communication:</em></span>​ You can text, FaceTime, or call when styling help is needed in a pinch! Whether you’re getting dressed in the morning, or in the evening for date night, or need an interview outfit, I’ll make myself available to get you where you need to go looking and feeling your best!
    </p>

    <p class="sub-service service__conditions">
      <em>I’m also available to travel for out of town clients. Please be aware that travel costs including flight, hotel accommodations, and meals will be added to this package price dependent on location and number of days needed.</em>
    </p>
  </article>

